Conference on Transitional Justice in Zimbabwe.  
</p>
<p>10. At the sixty-eighth session of the General Assembly, at which the Special 
Rapporteur presented his report on the interrelationship of transitional justice and 
development (A/68/345), he was a panellist in side events on &#8220;Teaching history in divided 
societies&#8221; and &#8220;Transitional justice and development: new agenda, concepts and 
possibilities&#8221;.  
</p>
