development agenda, organized by the Dag Hammarskj&#246;ld Foundation.  
14. In May 2014, the Special Rapporteur convened an expert meeting with prosecutors 
on the issue of prosecutorial strategies in the aftermath of atrocities, hosted by Sweden. In 
June, he took part in an NGO-expert round table on the same topic in Geneva.  
</p>
